cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.CL 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it focuses on multimedia retrieval using hashing techniques. It also involves deep learning (cs.LG) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as key components of the proposed method. Additionally, it may fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) and computational linguistics (cs.CL) sub-categories due to the nature of the data being processed and the potential applications in natural language processing.
